# This Vercel deploy targets the PUBLIC static tour + demo (/tour, /demo),
# which need no backend. The ~215MB of pre-generated practice audio is only
# used by the authenticated app (which redirects to /auth on a static
# deploy), so we exclude it to keep deploys small and fast.
#
# NOTE: the /demo "Listen (native voice)" button plays a handful of native
# reference clips. Those live in `public/demo-audio/` (a small, dedicated
# copy) precisely so they are NOT caught by the exclusions below and DO ship
# with this deploy. Do not add demo playback assets under `public/audio/`.
#
# The prebuild audio-consistency check only reads data/audio_index.json, so
# excluding these directories does not affect the build.
audio/
public/audio/
